text: Carl Magne Rønnevig (30 October 1874 - after 1946) was a Norwegian physician and politician. Rønnevig was born in Haugesund to ship owner Knud Hansen Rønnevig and Karen Margrethe Magnesen. He was elected representative to the Stortinget for the period 1931-1933, for the Liberal Party. ==References== Category:1874 births Category:Year of death missing Category:People from Haugesund Category:Liberal Party (Norway) politicians Category:Members of the Storting
